    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 6th level, you can move in sudden, swaying ways. You gain the following benefits.</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Leap to Your Feet\" data-source=\"XGE\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"1\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: Xanathar’s Guide to Everything, p34\">Leap to Your Feet</span></h3> <p>When you're &amp;Reference[condition=prone], you can stand up by spending 5 feet of movement, rather than half your speed.</p></div><div data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Redirect Attack\" data-source=\"XGE\" class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><h3 class=\"rd__h rd__h--2\" data-title-index=\"2\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner help-subtle\" title=\"Source: Xanathar’s Guide to Everything, p34\">Redirect Attack</span></h3> <p>When a creature misses you with a melee attack roll, you can spend 1 ki point as a reaction to cause that attack to hit one creature of your choice, other than the attacker, that you can see within 5 feet of you.</p></div></div></div>",
